{
  "stem": "27285.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] Believe me, nobody was anti-Russian then, [LAUGHS] because anything we could remember was that the Russian liberated us, so-- And Laura started to organize the children, and we-- and so-- and send us-- I don't know how-- anyway, to Czechoslovakia where we stayed in a recreational home and started to read and then recuperate and eat something and whatever.",
      "word_count": 60
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Where this I found here.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This is really funny, because a girlfriend, [INAUDIBLE], who stayed with me in Terezin, but she stayed behind in Terezin.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it was then Eva Diamontova.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't even know exactly what her family-- you know, in Israel, you only know first names usually, so it's Eva.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she's in [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she has this little album where any kid wrote something in.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, it was the habit to do.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And one of those is here.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So it says, [INAUDIBLE], [SPEAKING CZECH].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'll read it line by line and try to translate.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it's like Eva, life definitely is worth to live.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[SPEAKING CZECH].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's only necessary to give it content, or do you say content?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "To give it content.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[SPEAKING CZECH] If you should work with those possibilities that you have, you would definitely give it the best content.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[SPEAKING CZECH] Work according to your possibilities-- yes, possibilities-- and give away whatever you can.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[SPEAKING CZECH] Eva, remember sometimes at home-- underlined-- remember your cohabitant with whom you did a lot of-- have a lot of discussions, sometimes even quarreled.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I hope that you also liked Greta Hofmeister well.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that's it, and a few drawings accompany.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] is another-- oh, this is even earlier.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This is from '42.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Also Terezin, the 13th of July '42.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
